| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1206 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ba1d7ae9-d4b8-5645-a71a-33c3e6d91968"
